---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Ice Cream Social Success - JPMC Workers Alliance News">
  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Article Header -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-jpmc-blue to-jpmc-red p-8 text-white">
      <div class="flex items-center space-x-4 mb-4">
        <span class="text-sm font-medium bg-white bg-opacity-20 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">News</span>
        <time datetime="2025-07-15" class="text-sm opacity-90">July 15, 2025</time>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Ice Cream Social Success: Building Community Across Departments</h1>
      <p class="text-lg opacity-90">Our recent community building event brought together employees from across departments to discuss workplace improvements.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Article Content -->
    <div class="p-8">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Last week, the JPMC Workers Alliance hosted our largest community building event to date - an ice cream social that brought together over 150 employees from across different departments and office locations.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-jpmc-dark mb-4">Building Bridges Across Departments</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          The event was designed to break down silos and create connections between employees who might not normally interact during their daily work. We saw representatives from IT, Operations, Customer Service, and even some management-level employees who came to listen and learn.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-jpmc-blue mb-3">Key Discussions Included:</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-jpmc-red mr-2">•</span>
              Flexible work arrangements and remote work policies
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-jpmc-red mr-2">•</span>
              Compensation transparency and fair pay practices
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-jpmc-red mr-2">•</span>
              Workplace safety and health protocols
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-jpmc-red mr-2">•</span>
              Professional development and career advancement opportunities
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-jpmc-dark mb-4">Positive Feedback and Next Steps</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          The feedback from attendees was overwhelmingly positive. Many employees expressed appreciation for the opportunity to connect with colleagues from other departments and share their experiences and concerns in a safe, supportive environment.
        </p>

        <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-jpmc-gold pl-6 py-4 bg-yellow-50 mb-6">
          <p class="text-lg italic text-gray-700">
            "This was the first time I felt like my voice actually mattered. Meeting people from other departments made me realize we're all facing similar challenges. We're stronger together."
          </p>
          <cite class="text-sm text-gray-600">- Anonymous JPMC Employee</cite>
        </blockquote>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-jpmc-dark mb-4">Looking Forward</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          Based on the success of this event, we're planning to host similar community building activities on a regular basis. Our next event will focus on mental health and work-life balance, topics that emerged as priorities during our discussions.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-jpmc-dark text-white p-6 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Get Involved</h3>
          <p class="mb-4">
            Want to join us at our next event or help organize future activities? Contact us through Discord or email us at jpmcWorkers at gmail dot com.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
            <a href="https://discord.gg/BZA3pxppq9" class="bg-jpmc-blue hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-semibold py-2 px-4 rounded transition-colors text-center">
              Join Our Discord
            </a>
            <a href="/join-us" class="bg-jpmc-red hover:bg-red-700 text-white font-semibold py-2 px-4 rounded transition-colors text-center">
              Join the Alliance
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Article Footer -->
    <div class="bg-gray-50 px-8 py-6 border-t border-gray-200">
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-start sm:items-center">
        <div class="mb-4 sm:mb-0">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Published by JPMC Workers Alliance</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Tags: <span class="text-jpmc-blue">Community</span>, <span class="text-jpmc-blue">Events</span>, <span class="text-jpmc-blue">Workplace Culture</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex space-x-4">
          <a href="/news" class="text-jpmc-blue hover:text-blue-700 font-medium">← Back to News</a>
          <a href="/news/2025-06" class="text-jpmc-blue hover:text-blue-700 font-medium">Next Article →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout> 